# AI File Content Search Tool

A local semantic search tool that scans `.txt`, `.pdf`, and `.docx` files in a folder and finds content based on natural language queries.

This is part of an internship project at Indian Oil Corporation Limited (IOCL), PHLO Information Systems Department.

---

## 📌 Features

- Searches content across `.txt`, `.pdf`, `.docx` files
- Uses semantic similarity, not just keyword matching
- Shows file name, location (line/page/paragraph), similarity score, and a snippet
- Configurable via `config.yaml`

---

